le>   How to run a sucessful Fear portal break...lookin for advice</span><hr size=1> I know there was a link awhile back on runnin a sucessful portal break for Fear but I cant seem to find the post.  Can anyone direct me to it or offer some advice?  The portal break would be attempted by a guild that had planned a run in but the previous days raid had been canceled.  This seems to be happening frequently these days and any input would be appreciated.<br>
